                    <div class="FPTextHolder">
                        <h2><a href="/en/dep/ud/press/news/2010/diplomatic_presence.html?id=620269" title="">Changes in Norway’s diplomatic presence abroad</a></h2>
                        
                        <p>The Ministry of Foreign Affairs will increase its diplomatic presence in a number of countries in 2011, for example in Brazil, India, Indonesia, China and Russia. In order to free resources for these new missions, five missions will be closed, and there will be staff reductions at some other missions next year.</p>   
                        
                        
                        <p>
                            
                            (Ministry of Foreign Affairs, 05.10.2010) 
                        </p>            
                        
                    </div>
                </div>
            
                <div class="FPnewsHolder">
                    <div class="FPImgHolder">
                        
                        <a href="/en/dep/oed/press-center/Press-releases/2010/full-steam-ahead-on-the-norwegian-contin.html?id=619685" class="ISI_IGNORE">
