                        </a>
                        
                    </div>
                    <div class="FPTextHolder">
                        <h2><a href="/en/dep/oed/press-center/Press-releases/2010/full-steam-ahead-on-the-norwegian-contin.html?id=619685" title="">Full steam ahead on the Norwegian Continental Shelf</a></h2>
                        
                        <p>The activity level in the Norwegian petroleum industry is still high. Exploration activity has the last few years increased substantially and several new discoveries are being made. The Pension Fund is still growing, now approaching NOK 3000 billion. This is more than one million per family in Norway, says the Minister of Petroleum and Energy, Terje Riis-Johansen.</p>   
                        
                        
                        <p>
                            
                            (Ministry of Petroleum and Energy, 05.10.2010) 
                        </p>            
                        
                    </div>
                </div>
            
                <div class="FPnewsHolder">
                    <div class="FPImgHolder">
                        
                        <a href="/en/dep/fin/press-center/Press-releases/2010/new-strategy-council-for-the-government-.html?id=619587" class="ISI_IGNORE">
                            <img src="/Upload/FIN/Ingresssbilder/pressrelease.gif" alt="Illustration" class="" />
                        </a>
                        
                    </div>
                    <div class="FPTextHolder">
                        <h2><a href="/en/dep/fin/press-center/Press-releases/2010/new-strategy-council-for-the-government-.html?id=619587" title="">New Strategy Council for the Government Pension Fund Global</a></h2>
                        
                        <p>In the National Budget 2011 the Ministry today announced the establishment of a new Strategy Council with four external members. The Strategy Council has been asked to write a report on the long term investment strategy of the Government Pension Fund Global and present this no later than 1 December 2010.</p>   
                        
                        
                        <p>
                            
                            (Ministry of Finance, 05.10.2010) 
                        </p>            
                        
